overview: On August 13th GCW presents Homecoming 2022, Part 1 live on FITE. The event features GCW World Title Match where Jon Moxley defends his title against Effy. Who will be the new GCW World Champion?  Check the already announced lineup below:  Tag Team Match  The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) vs Los Macizos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo)  Death Match  John Wayne Murdoch vs Matt Tremont  Singles Match  Starboy Charlie vs Nick Wayne  GCW Ultraviolent Title Match  Alex Colon (c) vs Rina Yamashita  GCW World Title Match  Jon Moxley (c) vs Effy  *lineup subject to change
title: GCW Homecoming 2022, Part I
